XML::Document::Transport
------------------------

What is it?
-----------

The module builds and parses <Transport> document used by VOEvent Net and
the HTN for utility messages.

Requirements
------------

The module requires XML::Parser, XML::Writer and XML::Writer::String
and XML::Simple.

Installation
------------

Installation is automated using the ExtUtils::MakeMaker library

     % perl Makefile.PL
     % make
     % make test
     % make install

Authors
-------

The module was written by Alasdair Allan <aa@astro.ex.ac.uk>, of the 
University of Exeter Astrophysics Group (http://www.astro.ex.ac.uk/) 
as part of his work for the eSTAR project.

